CENG 5334 - Storm Water Pollution Control
This course provides students with the requirements of facilities that are
covered under the General of Multi-sector General (GMG) permit for
storm water discharges, as well as municipal facilities covered under a
Municipal Separate Stormwater Sewer System (MS4) permit and
construction erosion control. The course addresses prevention of storm
water pollution by teaching the Best Management Practices (BMPs) of
controlling and working with storm water.
Prerequisite: Department Chair approval.
